# RClinVarbitration source notices

## DuckDB C extension headers

`tools/ext/duckdb_capi/v1.5.3/` contains the DuckDB v1.5.3 C extension headers.
Their pinned upstream revision is recorded in `duckdb_headers.json`; DuckDB is
licensed under the MIT License.

## libxml2

The native extension links the host libxml2 library through `pkg-config`; it
does not bundle libxml2. libxml2 is MIT-licensed. The extension uses only the
forward-reader API and relies on its zlib-enabled XML.GZ support.

## ClinVar test fixture

`inst/extdata/VCV_XML_VCV000091629.xml.gz` is the public NCBI ClinVar sample
`VCV_XML_VCV000091629.xml`, downloaded from
`https://ftp.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pub/clinvar/xml/sample_xml/` and gzip-compressed
unchanged for exercising the production XML.GZ scan path.
